! :.config/X11/Xresources
! X colors.
*foreground:        #e6e6e6
*background:        #101010
*.foreground:       #e6e6e6
*.background:       #101010
emacs*foreground:   #e6e6e6
emacs*background:   #101010
URxvt*foreground:   #e6e6e6
XTerm*foreground:   #e6e6e6
UXTerm*foreground:  #e6e6e6
URxvt*background:   [100]#101010
