UXTerm*background:  #101010
URxvt*cursorColor:  #e3e3e3
XTerm*cursorColor:  #e3e3e3
UXTerm*cursorColor: #e3e3e3
URxvt*borderColor:  [100]#101010

! Colors 0-15.
